---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="About — GroupsMix"
  description="Learn about GroupsMix, the platform for discovering trusted social media groups."
>
<style is:inline>
        .legal-hero{text-align:center;padding:var(--space-8) 0 var(--space-4)}
        .legal-hero__icon{font-size:var(--text-5xl);margin-bottom:var(--space-3)}
        .legal-hero__subtitle{color:var(--text-secondary);margin-top:var(--space-2);max-width:560px;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;font-size:var(--text-base)}
        .glass-card{background:rgba(22,22,31,0.75);backdrop-filter:blur(16px);-webkit-backdrop-filter:blur(16px);border:1px solid rgba(42,42,62,0.6);border-radius:var(--radius-xl);padding:var(--space-6);box-shadow:0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);transition:transform .2s ease,box-shadow .2s ease}
        .glass-card:hover{box-shadow:0 12px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.3)}
        .glass-card__body{line-height:var(--leading-relaxed);color:var(--text-secondary)}
        .glass-card__body h2{color:var(--text-primary);margin:var(--space-6) 0 var(--space-3);font-size:var(--text-lg);font-weight:var(--font-bold);display:flex;align-items:center;gap:var(--space-2)}
        .glass-card__body h2::before{content:'';width:3px;height:20px;background:var(--accent-primary);border-radius:var(--radius-full);flex-shrink:0}
        .glass-card__body p{margin-bottom:var(--space-3)}
        .glass-card__body ul{margin-bottom:var(--space-4);padding-left:var(--space-4)}
        .glass-card__body ul li{margin-bottom:var(--space-2);line-height:1.6}
        .glass-card__body a{color:var(--accent-primary);text-decoration:none;font-weight:var(--font-medium)}
        .glass-card__body a:hover{text-decoration:underline}
        .legal-meta{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:var(--space-2);padding:var(--space-1) var(--space-3);background:rgba(108,92,231,0.1);border:1px solid rgba(108,92,231,0.2);border-radius:var(--radius-full);font-size:var(--text-xs);color:var(--accent-primary);font-weight:var(--font-semibold);margin-bottom:var(--space-6)}
        .legal-nav{display:flex;gap:var(--space-2);flex-wrap:wrap;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:var(--space-6)}
        .legal-nav a{padding:var(--space-2) var(--space-3);border-radius:var(--radius-full);border:1px solid var(--border-primary);background:var(--bg-card);color:var(--text-secondary);font-size:var(--text-sm);text-decoration:none;transition:all .15s ease}
        .legal-nav a:hover,.legal-nav a.active{background:var(--accent-primary);color:#fff;border-color:var(--accent-primary)}
        [data-theme="light"] .glass-card{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.75);border-color:rgba(200,200,220,0.5);box-shadow:0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.08)}
    </style>


        <div class="container" style="max-width:var(--container-md);padding:var(--space-8) var(--space-4)">
            <section class="legal-hero">
                <div class="legal-hero__icon">&#127758;</div>
                <h1>About GroupsMix</h1>
                <p class="legal-hero__subtitle">Building safer, more transparent online communities since day one.</p>
            </section>
            <nav class="legal-nav">
                <a href="/terms">Terms</a>
                <a href="/privacy">Privacy</a>
                <a href="/about">About</a>
                <a href="/faq">FAQ</a>
                <a href="/contact">Contact</a>
                <a href="/support">Support Center</a>
            </nav>
            <div class="glass-card">
                <div class="glass-card__body">
                    <p style="font-size:var(--text-lg);color:var(--text-primary);margin-bottom:var(--space-6)">GroupsMix is the leading platform for discovering, verifying, and joining trusted social media groups across WhatsApp, Telegram, Discord, and more. We connect people with genuine communities while keeping the ecosystem safe from fraud.</p>

                    <h2>Our Mission</h2>
                    <p>We believe every online community deserves visibility and trust. Our mission is to build the most reliable directory of social media groups &mdash; powered by intelligent algorithms that rank quality and filter out fraud, so users find genuine communities and group owners reach the right audience.</p>

                    <h2>What We Do</h2>
                    <p>GroupsMix provides a comprehensive suite of tools and services for both group seekers and group owners:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Curate &amp; Verify</strong> &mdash; Every group is reviewed before listing to ensure authenticity and quality.</li>
                        <li><strong>Community Reviews</strong> &mdash; Real users rate and review groups, helping others make informed decisions.</li>
                        <li><strong>Trust Scoring</strong> &mdash; Our proprietary Trust Score algorithm evaluates verification, ratings, reports, and engagement.</li>
                        <li><strong>Scam Protection</strong> &mdash; Built-in Scam Wall, encrypted links, and behavioral fraud detection keep users safe.</li>
                        <li><strong>Promotion Tools</strong> &mdash; VIP plans and visibility boosters help group owners grow their audience.</li>
                        <li><strong>AI-Powered Tools</strong> &mdash; Free tools for group name generation, scam detection, privacy auditing, and more.</li>
                    </ul>

                    <h2>The GXP System</h2>
                    <p>Our GroupsMix Experience Points (GXP) system rewards active community members for their contributions:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Earn GXP</strong> by submitting groups, writing reviews, reporting scams, and engaging with the platform.</li>
                        <li><strong>Level up</strong> to unlock badges, enhanced visibility, and exclusive perks.</li>
                        <li><strong>Build reputation</strong> &mdash; higher GXP signals trustworthiness to the community.</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p>GXP is designed to encourage genuine participation and reward users who make the platform better for everyone.</p>

                    <h2>Trust &amp; Safety</h2>
                    <p>Every group goes through our multi-layer review process before appearing on the platform:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Manual &amp; automated review</strong> of all group submissions for content quality and authenticity.</li>
                        <li><strong>Trust Score algorithm</strong> that factors in verification status, community ratings, report history, and engagement metrics.</li>
                        <li><strong>Encrypted group links</strong> that are only revealed after verification checks.</li>
                        <li><strong>Community reporting</strong> system with rapid response to flagged content.</li>
                        <li><strong>Row-Level Security (RLS)</strong> and zero personal data storage to protect user privacy.</li>
                    </ul>

                    <h2>Supported Platforms</h2>
                    <p>GroupsMix supports groups from all major social and messaging platforms, including:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>WhatsApp</li>
                        <li>Telegram</li>
                        <li>Discord</li>
                        <li>Facebook Groups</li>
                        <li>Viber</li>
                        <li>And more platforms added regularly.</li>
                    </ul>

                    <h2>Get Involved</h2>
                    <p>Whether you are looking to discover new communities or promote your own group, GroupsMix is here to help. Here is how to get started:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li><a href="/search">Browse groups</a> by platform, category, country, or language.</li>
                        <li><a href="/submit">Submit your group</a> for free listing and community exposure.</li>
                        <li><a href="/faq">Read our FAQ</a> for answers to common questions.</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p>Have questions or need help? <a href="/contact">Contact us</a> or visit the <a href="/support">Support Center</a>.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    
</BaseLayout>
